The old gods have forgotten this land. No one could save our people when
darkness started spreading and collecting human souls for its army. Odallus
is a classic exploration/action game, inspired by Ghosts'n Goblins, Demon's
Crest and Castlevania. Player takes place of Haggis, a warrior tired of fight
who must wield his sword once more to rescue his son from Darkness.

Eight levels open to exploration
Stunning 8-bit graphics
Dark fantasy atmosphere
4+ hours of gameplay
50+ types of enemies

GOG Page: https://www.gog.com/game/odallus_the_dark_call

